lead_paragraph: With her team playing its second road game in three days, coach Cori Close was just hoping UCLA would find a way to get better against North Carolina A&T on the Aggies' home court.

headline.print_headline: No. 10 UCLA Women Rout North Carolina A&T, 83-42
